{"tid":1173463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本8月起限制海外投資電訊業","createTime":"2019-05-27T06:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T06:41:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0119f2f2e041d451562c9914267456d06719a6","tid":1173463,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"美國封殺華為風波不斷擴大之際，作為美國盟友的日本，將限制海外投資電訊業。<br />\n<br />\n日本宣布，從8月起將訊息技術和電訊行業加入外資在日企持股限制的行業清單。<br />\n<br />\n財務省表示，由於對網絡安全的疑慮升高，政府會限制對20個IT行業的直接投資，包括內存晶片製造商，手機製造商，電腦，電訊設備等。<br />\n<br />\n根據法規，外資對日本企業的參股以及其他投資會遭受限制。海外投資者獲得上市公司10%或以上的股權，或對非上市公司的特定投資，將受到監管審查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2147210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2147210&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=478625e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2147210</a>"},{"pid":"5a0c6196c07c5640106eea2f450c419a6dcb64e0","tid":1173463,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:39:48.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"191647c86802577858251d80336824280acb6c03","tid":1173463,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"針對強國居多（寶島除外？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}